sect1.para:
Let's first create the patch-queue branch and import the
      contents of debian/patches onto it using
      &gbp-pq;

listitem.para:
Launch an import. If there's nothing to import &gbp-pq; will just
	create an empty branch and switch your working copy to it:

  &gbp-pq-import;

sect1.para:
The patch-queue branch can also be re-created when pulling (this
will additionally drop your current patch-queue branch and recreate it
from debian/patches):
